        }
        .body{
            background-color: #f6f3fb;
            font-family: monospace;
            width:100%;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .wish{
            text-align: right;
            padding-right: 20%;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .captch{
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #2aaeb3;
            font-weight: 900;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style='width:100%'>
<div class="body">
    <p class="ifsystitle">独孤九剑系统</p>
    <div class="mailBox">
        <p>你好:<p>
        <p class="content">
            你正在用微信登陆独孤九剑系统<br>本次收到的验证码是:<br><span class="captch">${captcha}</span><br>有效时间120分钟,请尽快验证
        </p>
    </div>
    <p class="wish">祝工作愉快!</p>
</div>
